<section class="access">
  <div class="access-wapper">
    <h2>所在地・アクセス</h2>
    <div class="access-flex-wrap">
      <div class="map">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d13053.469377808036!2d136.9505155152385!3d35.122505445605086!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x60037b8125f7c96d%3A0x711594c47beb1825!2z6aCt44G744GQ44GX5bCC6ZaAIHJlc2V0!5e0!3m2!1sja!2sjp!4v1693278348042!5m2!1sja!2sjp"
          width="100%"
          height="400"
          style="border:0;"
          allowfullscreen=""
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="access-text">
        <address>
          〒468-0066<br />
          愛知県名古屋市天白区元八事1-107<br />
          ナチュール元八事「リライフ治療院」内
        </address>
        <p>駐車場：治療院前に3台分有り(<span class="bold">13･15･16</span>)</p>
        <p>※ <span class="bold">「リライフ治療院」様院内</span>の個室にて施術しております</p>
        <p>
          ご予約・お問い合わせ等につきましては、リライフ治療院では承ることはできません。
        </p>
        <p>必ず当店までご連絡ください。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="clinic">
    <div class="clinic-flex-wrap">
      <div class="clinic-text">
        <h3 class="clinic-name">リライフ治療院</h3>
        <p>明るく温かい雰囲気の治療院です。</p>
        <p>玄関を開けるとホッとする、そんな空間です。</p>
        <p>
          完全個室のプライベート空間で、<br>ゆっくり落ち着いた癒しの時間を<br>お過ごしくださいませ。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="slider-group">
        <div class="clinic-image">
          <img src="/clinic_image_1.jpg" alt="外観" width="400" height="auto" />
        </div>
        <div class="clinic-image">
          <img src="/clinic_image_2.jpg" alt="内観1" width="400" height="auto"/>
        </div>
        <div class="clinic-image">
          <img src="/clinic_image_3.jpg" alt="内観2" width="400" height="auto"/>
        </div>
        <div class="clinic-image">
          <img src="/clinic_image_4.jpg" alt="個室" width="400" height="auto"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <style>
      .access {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        padding-inline: 1.6rem;
        padding-block: 40px;
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color:var(--bgSecondary);
      }

      h2 {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .access-flex-wrap {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 24px;
        margin-top: 64px;
        /* margin-bottom: 64px; */
      }

      .map {
        text-align: center;
        flex-grow: 1;
      }

      address {
        padding-block-end: 40px;
      }
      .access-text {
        flex-grow: 1;
      }

      .access-text p {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        padding: .8rem 0;
      }

      address {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        font-style: normal;
      }

      h3 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .clinic-name {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .clinic-name::before, .clinic-name::after {
        content:"";
        background-color: black;
        height: 1px;
        width:40px;
      }

      .clinic-name::before {
        margin-right: 40px;
      }

      .clinic-name::after {
        margin-left: 40px;
      }

      .clinic {
        width: 100%;
        padding-block: 40px;
      }

      .clinic-text p {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        /* padding: 0.8rem 0; */
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 250%;
      }

      .clinic-flex-wrap {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column; /* PCではrowに */
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 24px;
      }

      .slider-group {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: nowrap;
        overflow: hidden;
        overflow-x: auto;
        gap: 16px;
        scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
      }

      .clinic-image {
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        width: 300px;
        height: 225px;
        scroll-snap-align: start;
      }

      .clinic-image img{
        width: 100%;
      }

      @media screen and (900px <= width) {
        .access-flex-wrap {
          flex-direction: row;
          justify-content: center;
          gap: 40px;
        }

        .map {
          width: 430px;
        }

        .access-text {
          width: 430px;
        }

        .clinic-flex-wrap {
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: row;
        }

        .clinic-text {
          width: 430px;
        }

        .slider-group {
          width: 430px;
        }

        .clinic-image {
        width: 400px;
        height: 300px;
      }
      }
    </style>
  </div>
</section>
